OL,3,C'I'm free': Asylum seeker learns
OL,4,CEnglish thanks to donated laptop
OL,6,FAn asylum seeker who arrived in the UK
OL,7,Fnine months ago, with no possessions,
OL,8,Fsays the gift of a computer has
OL,9,Ftransformed his and his family's lives.
OL,11,FMohammad Saleem Nezami was an IT
OL,12,Fexpert in Afghanistan before the
OL,13,FTaliban seized back power three years
OL,14,Fago and the family fled to the UK.
OL,16,FThe laptop was given to him by the
OL,17,Fcharity SOFEA, based in Didcot, South-
OL,18,FOxfordshire, which repairs and
OL,19,Frecycles unwanted laptops and phones.
