OL,3,C'I'm free': Asylum seeker learns
OL,4,CEnglish thanks to donated laptop
OL,6,FHe says the donated laptop has been
OL,7,Fcritical in him learning to speak
OL,8,FEnglish and register his children with
OL,9,Fthe local school and GP surgery.
OL,11,FMohammad Saleem Nezami said: "The
OL,12,Fcomputer is the only thing that made
OL,13,Fme able to connect with other worlds,
OL,14,Fpeople and knowledge.
OL,16,F"I study four and five hours a day on
OL,17,Fthe computer researching, making all
OL,18,Fthe choices in my life.
