OL,3,C'I'm free': Asylum seeker learns
OL,4,CEnglish thanks to donated laptop
OL,6,F"I should register my children with
OL,7,Fthe GP, the school and other
OL,8,Forganisations, also I received an
OL,9,Femail from Home Office, but I didn't
OL,10,Fhave a computer to say what is in the
OL,11,Femail.
OL,13,F"When I was given the computer, I told
OL,14,Fthem, 'I am free'."
OL,16,FThe SOFEA project was set up during
OL,17,Flockdown and is now being expanded
OL,18,Fthanks to a #100,000 funding grant
OL,19,Ffrom tech giant Virgin Media and the
OL,20,FEnvironmental charity HubBub.
