OL,6,FGet Oxfordshire Online, Project
OL,7,FManager Ben Tuppen said: "We work with
OL,8,Fcharities and community groups
OL,9,Fsupporting people who can't get online
OL,10,Fand finding out what their needs are.
OL,12,F"It could be as simple as providing an
OL,13,Fold-style nokia phone with a sim card
OL,14,Fso you have a number you can put on a
OL,15,FCV when looking for a job.
